name: Brutal - Paws of Fury [SG]
description:
Brutal: Paws of Fury is an arcade-fighting game developed by Eurocom and GameTek. It came out on 01-10-1994. It was published by GameTek. The game is rated as "Meh" on RAWG.
Brutal: Paws of Fury is available on Commodore / Amiga, SEGA CD, SEGA 32X and SNES.
